

Demo #1: Getting DB under a version control
-------------------------------------------
Initially we have 1 production database and we want to get it under version control with dbmake.



Demo #2: Creating another DB
----------------------------
Additionally to the first DB we want to add another instance of the database for test deployment.

dbmake 



